148
00:22:22,490 --> 00:22:25,100
Promiňte, pane doktore.

149
00:22:25,940 --> 00:22:27,780
Jung Hye.

150
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:33,810
Tady.

151
00:22:43,250 --> 00:22:45,040
Jung Hye!

152
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:48,280
Jung Hye!

153
00:22:49,770 --> 00:22:51,780
Pane doktore.

154
00:22:58,420 --> 00:23:01,950
Ale ne...

155
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,280
Jung Hye.

156
00:24:42,980 --> 00:24:45,040
Je v šoku.

157
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:52,600
Prostě sem vtrhněte, kreténi!

158
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:54,700
Co vám tak trvá?

159
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:58,700
<i>Kim Yo Hane, jsou tu rodiče Eun Sung.</i>

160
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:27,920
Tahle? Je to ta nabitá?

161
00:25:31,910 --> 00:25:36,000
Jedna z nich určitě.

162
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:40,320
Eun sung.

163
00:25:48,710 --> 00:25:52,080
Jsem rád, že se odsud dostaneš první.

164
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:17,550
Eun Sung.

165
